node.text: So much of my inspiration in climbing and life has come from incredible women who came before me. Their stories of grit, passion, and creativity were a pivotal part of the paths I chose in my own life. Such stories have a ripple effect that spread throughout our society and continue to inspire future generations ✨ Proud to take part in this conversation with my biggest supporter and favorite human @adrianballinger to honor @imyourwomanmovie premiering Friday Dec. 11th on @amazonprimevideo #imyourwoman

node.title: Amazon Studios I'M YOUR WOMAN Conversation Series

node.text:
Honored to have been a part of the film #WorldDebut highlighting the three new Olympic sports (🧗🏼‍♀️🏄🏽🛹✨🙌🏻) AND I got to hang w the amazing @kyra_condie during filming who will be representing the 🇺🇸 in climbing’s first ever Olympic Games 🥰💪🏼

What was once an activity practiced by a few on the outskirts of society is now making it's #worlddebut as climbing enters the Olympic arena along with skateboarding and surfing. Learn the decades long story of how these sports made it to the world stage in the latest film #worlddebut now live on @youtube. Watch now at link in bio 😬😬😬

Produced by @wzrdmedia , @boardwalkpictures. Directed by @colesax and @gknowproductions. Executive Produced by @tonyhawk. @olympics
